David Jones , chief executive officer
of Havas SA, and author of "Who Cares Wins," discusses using 
social media as a tool in running a successful and responsible 
business. Jones talks with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and Courtney 
Donohoe on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:23
 